comments: Jackson Jr. (MEM) goes to, not through, Morris Sr.'s (LAC) space and marginal contact occurs as Jackson Jr. releases away during the drive.
Morris Sr. (LAC) moves alongside Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.

Jackson Jr. (MEM) brings his arm forward and brushes George's (LAC) head as marginal contact occurs when George gathers the rebound. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Westbrook (LAC) maintains his arms within the frame of his body and does not deliver illegal contact to Kennard (MEM) during the pick.
Bane (MEM) is not established in a legal guarding position in Leonard's (LAC) path and is moving laterally when contact occurs.
Kennard (MEM) firms up in a screening position in George's (LAC) path and does not deliver contact.
George (LAC) brings his arm toward Bane's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs at the start of Bane's drive.
Gordon (LAC) extends his arm forward and initiates contact to Bane (MEM) that affects his SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
Westbrook (LAC) brings his arm toward Tillman (MEM) and marginal contact occurs as Westbrook releases away to roll.
Tillman (MEM) and Gordon (LAC) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Gordon (LAC) brings his arm toward Tillman's (MEM) space and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Kennard (LAC) rests his forearm to Westbrook's (LAC) side and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.

George (LAC) makes contact with the ball as he goes for the rebound and marginal arm contact occurs with Jackson Jr. (MEM).  Jackson Jr. loses his balance as a result of coming together with his teammate Kennard (MEM).
Bane (MEM) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during George's (LAC) layup attempt.
George (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Jackson Jr. (MEM) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) commits a foul on Leonard (LAC).
Westbrook (LAC) avoids making body contact with Jackson Jr. (MEM) as he contests the jump shot attempt.
